The world 's joint third-largest cruise ship , the Anthem of the Seas , has just arrived in Southampton , UK .
Ahead of its naming ceremony on April 20 , the mammoth ocean liner has reached its berth : the 101 in Southampton Docks , will be its home port for the summer season .
The new ship has a bar operated by robots that mix cocktails using precise ingredients .
The cruise ship has capacity for almost 5,000 passengers at a time .